        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Support International Criminal Investigations for Ukraine Act</b></p> <p>This bill repeals a provision that prohibits using federal funds to support the International Criminal Court (ICC). Specifically, the provision prohibits such funding unless the United States becomes a party to the ICC pursuant to a treaty.</p>]]>
        </text>
